reviews.text: It is a fast food joint. The menu is quite elaborate. The price is reasonable. The food is tasty. It is famous for its barbecue meat. Definitely a place to go for a quick bite but not a place you want to linger.
The food was good. Especially the goose! Portions were of average size and well prepared. Nothing was too salty or too bland.

We go here most evenings when back in Sheung Shui. Good selection of dishes at reasonable prices. Never had a bad experience yet. Can get very busy early evenings. Check out the roast duck and char sui counter. Takeaways available.
Easy to find a table during lunch hours
Mostly you don't feel you are local at all.

result.name: 太興

reviews.text: It is a fast food joint. The menu is quite elaborate. The price is reasonable. The food is tasty. It is famous for its barbecue meat. Definitely a place to go for a quick bite but not a place you want to linger.
快靚正下午茶餐,餐蛋飯😀
今日食晏，䌓忙時段待應們都好有禮貌
食物，賣相精緻，好味道，價格中等，場地佈置，別殊一格！😀😄😍
上水分店這家真喺好唔掂，先前曾投訴到他們客服，最近再去光顧，原想點燒味飯，咁橋望到個切燒味師傅嘅手水腫兼且唔帶手套徒手去攞燒味來切，個口罩跌到落條頸度，仲不停咁大聲講野噴口水，感覺有點反胃，所以點咗個牛丸湯米，點知咸到苦，見到有滾水加多一倍始能入口，後來跟部長阿姐投訴，她講已經知道，搞到我仲興，希望上水這家早點關門算啦！
